com.versant.var.receiver
Class VARRequest

java.lang.Object
  com.versant.var.receiver.VARRequest

public class VARRequest
extends java.lang.Object

The Java wrapper for the replication request created by the request engine. It represents the set of objects that belong to a single channel, updated in one transaction.

See Also:
VARTxRequest, VARTxMessage, VARTxRequestProcessor
